snippet.title: Stratovarius - Forever (Cover by SIEG)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial
Symmetric Chaos Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SymmetricChaos

새해 복 많이 받으세요!

Stephen Kim is one of the great guitarists in Korea and has a very good personality. We covered Rainbow In The Dark and it turned out really well, so I wanted him work with me so bad. Unfortunately, he lived miles away, hence working together was not that easy. In fact, I might gave him a lot of pressure by asking him to make a live film with this song. I hope really again, I could have some chances to work with him sometime in the future and this video will be a great encouragement for him as well.

Abandoned Project 04
Stratovarius - Forever (Covered in 2015)

Besides the band album, I’ve been releasing music works just little by little, but there are not so many projects given to the audience in the 12 years since I started YouTube.

Sometimes I couldn't make my instrumental track, my songs weren't up to the level of publication, or problems with other musicians.

There are countless songs that haven't seen the light regardless of the cover and the original.

However, something triggered me to start thinking that I should approach the listener more even with my incomplete work.

Now I take my courage to open my imperfect voice that I never share before.

It's little bit more aggressive than the original version and it's been also my intention to make this cover an individual thing and not a direct copy of the original vocals. It's up to you to decide whether the attempt has been successful or not.

If you like this song, please visit my facebook page.
Thank You.
